<plot>While all that glitters is not gold, Burmas tourism industry is booming. The generals of a brutal dictatorship who are holding the country in thrall are pleased by this fact. In the course of a fictitious all-inclusive trip the country is examined from all possible and impossible perspectives in a look behind its exotic facade.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087098</url></doc>
